name: Allen Frances
content:
ECT most effective treatment for very severe #depression.
Underused because of #stigma & lack of availability.
Quick & dramatic response in about 80% of patients.
Continuation treatment w meds or maintenance ECT necessary to prevent relapse.
What I would choose for me. https://twitter.com/judyskt/status/1111903044751577090 …
